   <text>
      <body>
         <div>
            <head>17.7.1884 Donnerstag</head>
            <p>
               <placeName type="write" key="49127">Kreuznach</placeName>
               <note type="reg">Bad Kreuznach</note> July 17. 1884.</p>
            <p>
               <persName key="103">Mamma&#x2019;s</persName> birthday. Gave her a vase. Went shooting at
               the Kaiserau. Great row in <placeName key="49096">Paris</placeName> on Monday. German
               flags torn down and burnt before the <name type="work" key="36620">statue of Strasburg</name>
               <note type="reg">
                  <persName key="80960">Pradier</persName>
               </note>, a revolution impending in <placeName key="48887">England</placeName>.
               Conflict between the houses over the Reform bill. German papers crying for war
               against <placeName key="48914">France</placeName>. Cholera bad in <placeName key="48914">France</placeName>. Altogether very gloomy prospects on all sides.
                  <orgName key="67231">Hotel Continental</orgName> windows broken on account of German flags
               by the mob and <persName key="8642">Deroulède</persName> In the evening went on the
               water to the corso and fireworks. A man fell into the water and <persName key="104">Gee</persName> got very excited about it. It rained very much</p>
         </div>
